#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:2 34536d85f5494f3d97bc8f05c1a37038
msgid "外设"
msgstr "Peripherals"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:17 3e46f95abc0748f1ac9f88bde45c469a
msgid "ADC的精度和采样率是多少？"
msgstr "What are the ADC resolution and sampling rate?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:18 ee5eb220a93d4d508d540458d4611809
msgid "ADC实际精度为12BIT,当OSR=256,打开平均值滤波的时候可以达到16bit精度。 当ADC工作在非多通道扫描模式时,最大可支持2M采样率。 如果是多通道扫描模式，最大支持1M采样率。"
msgstr "The actual ADC resolution is 12-bit. When OSR=256 and average filtering is enabled, it can reach 16-bit resolution. When the ADC works in non-multi-channel scan mode, the maximum supported sampling rate is 2M. In multi-channel scan mode, the maximum supported sampling rate is 1M."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:23 d523f49274cd4d168efb332b3afae319
msgid "mtimer的作用是什么，它是如何工作的？"
msgstr "What is the function of mtimer and how does it work?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:24 b5b8a65ca7094ddbab83c8f3655590b0
msgid "MTimer为内核提供的一个timer，开启后实现计时功能，计数值与比较值寄存器位于内核，使用方式与一般timer无明显区别。"
msgstr "MTimer is a timer provided by the core. After it is enabled, it provides timing functionality. The counter value and compare value registers are located in the core. Its usage is not significantly different from a normal timer."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:27 1b166e6d0a4f41ab89b82dab1619f2c4
msgid "模组包含几个timer?"
msgstr "How many timers does the module contain?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:28 054e32a43e814569a61a27df59988e31
msgid "1个64-bit mtimer，2个32-bit normal timer，1个16-bit watchdog timer。"
msgstr "It contains one 64-bit mtimer, two 32-bit normal timers, and one 16-bit watchdog timer."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:32 3776ff04f8f04918b39e684a530ad292
msgid "看门狗的超时时间如何设置？超时的现象是什么？"
msgstr "How is the watchdog timeout set? What happens when it times out?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:33 edbb6c14052c4d63b070973e763f9bb4
msgid "看门狗包含一个计数器和比较器，通过写入比较器的值，当计数器向上计数达到比较器的值时，会产生一个看门狗中断信号或者一个系统复位信号， 具体产生哪种信号由用户自行设置。"
msgstr "The watchdog includes a counter and a comparator. By writing a value to the comparator, when the counter counts upward and reaches the comparator value, a watchdog interrupt signal or a system reset signal will be generated. Which signal is generated is configured by the user."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:38 69d9e9cfc06548ec9192e19844a7ad3f
msgid "GPIO的配置参数有哪些？如何配置？"
msgstr "What are the GPIO configuration parameters? How are they configured?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:39 86509980ad7846558e0d39c642fadede
msgid "gpioPin : GPIO pin number， GPIO编号 gpioFun : GPIO function， GPIO功能 gpioMode : input/output/af， 输入/输出/复用模式 pullType : pull_up/pull_down/pull_none， 上拉/下拉/浮空 drive : drive strength， 驱动能力， 数值越大驱动能力越强 smtCtrl : smt, 迟滞控制，建议设一 详情参见低RM GPIO章节。"
msgstr "gpioPin: GPIO pin number. gpioFun: GPIO function. gpioMode: input/output/af, input/output/alternate function mode. pullType: pull_up/pull_down/pull_none, pull-up/pull-down/floating. drive: drive strength; the larger the value, the stronger the drive capability. smtCtrl: smt, hysteresis control, recommended to be set to 1. For details, refer to the GPIO section of the RM."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:45 f5f18245fe94411495572a16b3d44357
msgid "GPIO的引脚在使用时有什么需要注意的？"
msgstr "What should be noted when using GPIO pins?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:46 971f3187d34f4906bbf2e53647608881
msgid "需要正确配置GPIO结构体，不建议同时使能input与output。"
msgstr "The GPIO structure must be configured correctly. It is not recommended to enable input and output at the same time."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:50 12f861b738fc4dc8b52e62f669bd56d3
msgid "SPI一次最多发送多少字节？发送机制是什么？"
msgstr "What is the maximum number of bytes that SPI can send at one time? What is the transmission mechanism?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:51 63dd11ad87d149d3abf3bd5909792a21
msgid "SPI一次可发送任意长度个字节，只需要保持tx fifo中有持续可用的数据，另外tx fifo的宽度可根据需要设置为8/16/24/32-bit。 发送机制是：使能spi发送功能之后，tx fifo中的数据会按照设定的位宽和bit顺序进入移位寄存器中，然后按照极性和相位的设置在每一个时钟的上升沿/下降沿去改变MISO/MOSI的引脚电平将数据发送出去。 例如CPOL=1，CPHA=1，则SPI时钟空闲时为高电平，数据在时钟的上升沿被送出。"
msgstr "SPI can send any number of bytes at one time, as long as there is continuously available data in the tx fifo. In addition, the width of the tx fifo can be set to 8/16/24/32-bit as needed. The transmission mechanism is: after enabling the SPI transmit function, data in the tx fifo enters the shift register according to the configured bit width and bit order, and then, according to the polarity and phase settings, the MISO/MOSI pin level is changed on each rising/falling edge of the clock to send the data out. For example, when CPOL=1 and CPHA=1, the SPI clock is high when idle, and data is output on the rising edge of the clock."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:57 d0a6575542e64260b474b7259560e576
msgid "模组是否支持播放/录音的功能，支持哪些常用的频率和位宽？"
msgstr "Does the module support playback/recording functions? What common frequencies and bit widths are supported?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:58 ca044a19f7454284accf6b91437ee065
msgid "模组内置12-bit ADC以及10-bit DAC，可以通过ADC和DAC的基本功能配合推荐的功放/录音电路，完成播放和录音的功能。 仅支持8K常用采样率16-bit位宽播放，因为DAC的时钟仅支持32K 16K 8K 512K四种采样率可选，没有专业的audio PLL ，只有8K是常用的播放采样率，其他采样率不常用。"
msgstr "The module has a built-in 12-bit ADC and 10-bit DAC. Playback and recording functions can be implemented through the basic functions of the ADC and DAC together with the recommended power amplifier/recording circuit. Only 8K common sampling rate and 16-bit bit-width playback are supported. Because the DAC clock only supports four optional sampling rates: 32K, 16K, 8K, and 512K, and there is no dedicated audio PLL. Only 8K is a common playback sampling rate; the other sampling rates are not commonly used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:62 bea5e25924574a6e98a48a12436fb7eb
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F模组的AT串口可以关闭作为普通UART通讯口么？"
msgstr "Can the AT serial port of the Ai-WB2-12F module be disabled and used as a normal UART communication port?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:63 70bb50a2fff9420ebec116ab58fed477
msgid "可以的，需要做二次开发。"
msgstr "Yes, secondary development is required."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:66 568a7d27980c4aeb89b28f547cb63010
msgid "WB2系列的开发上NC引脚是做啥用的"
msgstr "What are the NC pins on WB2 series development boards used for?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:67 2fe5396eb2e146a58d7603be2f80c69f
msgid "NC表示没有引出该引脚，无法使用"
msgstr "NC means that the pin is not routed out and cannot be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:70 9045666608dd40f3adde281cd9b24737
msgid "WB2系列模组带USB接口吗"
msgstr "Do WB2 series modules have a USB interface?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:71 09833bbfedfa44038f86441355f8c968
msgid "不带，模组内部的芯片没有USB相关的引脚接口"
msgstr "No. The chip inside the module does not have USB-related pins or interfaces."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:74 1a686282b3eb40858c6297ff4b3a1a26
msgid "请问WB2-12F模组（AT固件）支持硬件流控么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-12F module with AT firmware support hardware flow control?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:75 769eaf4fba174063b3aa6b8e58f55bec
msgid "不支持；"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:78 8208b186e7b7428a93c0433001a1b018
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F的ADC是多少位的"
msgstr "How many bits is the ADC of Ai-WB2-12F?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:79 998166dc5ea540cf9570d0b9cfae818b
msgid "ADC为8位"
msgstr "The ADC is 8-bit."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:82 0d8c4c07df654e428ed5c83fef319748
msgid "请问Ai-WB2-07S模组是否支持SPI接口AT指令驱动控制？"
msgstr "Does the Ai-WB2-07S module support SPI-interface AT command control?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:83 3cdadce881de45759940557b8cd7244b
msgid "不支持，出厂固件仅支持串口"
msgstr "No. The factory firmware only supports UART."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:86 e72d5eb17c7a43bd9cc960ab1edfb4dc
msgid "WB2系列模组的EN引脚有没有必要用三极管实现控制？"
msgstr "Is it necessary to use a transistor to control the EN pin of WB2 series modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:87 cdba94ee640e4e4e90e25277dcb8148f
msgid "不需要。"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:90 ea114fb6ff2049ddb0890bd0d217b1b4
msgid "WB2-32S开发板有几个串口可以使用，为什么好多引脚都是NC"
msgstr "How many UART ports are available on the WB2-32S development board? Why are many pins NC?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:91 0c78b61e20394b9b9a65148182ccf2b2
msgid "开发板有2个串口可以使用，通过软件定义实现，NC引脚表示该引脚为悬空引脚，不可使用"
msgstr "The development board has 2 UART ports available, implemented through software definition. NC pins indicate floating pins and cannot be used."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:94 322927fd495446f1ab46bbcd4309df2e
msgid "WB2系列的串口支持硬件流控吗"
msgstr "Do the UART ports of WB2 series support hardware flow control?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:95 674ff73b68fd4043b59cf6c025c8e833
msgid "需做开发实现，默认不支持硬件流控"
msgstr "It needs to be implemented through development. Hardware flow control is not supported by default."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:98 6b28f08842d14aacb5ac29fe1a058575
msgid "请问WB2-32S模组没有SDIO接口么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-32S module not have an SDIO interface?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:99 e10ec1b40c344e339ae2ba88c6e84d16
msgid "有的；"
msgstr "Yes, it does."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:103 ebe364f5d2df413698a97d8280cb7765
msgid "WB2-07S这个RST引脚和EN引脚有什么区别吗"
msgstr "What is the difference between the RST pin and EN pin of WB2-07S?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:104 b6af74b1e4114e73ac533d56a3dc694c
msgid "没有区别，只是模块默认通过EN引脚进行复位，如果需要通过RST进行复位需要修改模组内部硬件实现"
msgstr "There is no difference. The module resets through the EN pin by default. If reset through RST is required, the module's internal hardware needs to be modified."

